When this project is finished you can connect to Server with PHP.
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Current tasks:
  - Everything

To get started simply make a php file with this code:

<?php
require_once('MinecraftPHP.class.php');

new MinecraftPHP('yournickname', 'yourpassword', 'yourserverip');
?>

If you use an other port than the default (25565), specify it as 4th parameter.